King Baby Doge - Journey like a King

We are the new ""DOGE"" themed token that is not your typical meme token. Our token strives to be the best DOGE theme token among the rest. 100% Community Driven and Token's main function is the proprietary off-chain algorithmic smart buyback and high deflationary concept! 

King Baby Doge have an auto burn and auto buyback function in every single transactions, which means the longer you hold the more tokens you will earn. With 2% Charity distribution, which is happening twice a month, we worked together with Dogs Charity & Children in Need Charity. 

Our Roadmap is clear at kingbabydoge.io and with the marketing plan on phase, King Baby Doge is on the right track to be everyone's new Dogecoin!
